name: Dutch Bitcoin Asset Manager Blockrise Obtains MiCAR License for European Expansion
description: The grotesque lattice of the saint performs its kinetic liturgy, submitting to the MiCAR monolith. Through the heavy grain and volumetric fog, the sacred mandate is accepted; the cold cyan baptism of regulation transforms the decaying chrome into legitimate scripture.
